#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/legendre.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.legendre.legmul:33
msgid ""
"In general, the (polynomial) product of two C-series results in terms that "
"are not in the Legendre polynomial basis set.  Thus, to express the product "
"as a Legendre series, it is necessary to \"reproject\" the product onto said "
"basis set, which may produce \"unintuitive\" (but correct) results; see "
"Examples section below."
msgstr ""

